    "description": "Join the Groww Capital India family as a Credit Analyst in Rajkot. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout Groww Capital India:\nGroww Capital India is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Prepare and analyze financial statements, reports, and budgets\n• Develop financial models and projections for business planning\n• Liaise with banks, regulators, and financial institutions\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Chartered Accountant (ICAI)\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in QuickBooks\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in Credit Analysis\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Flexible working hours\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Company-sponsored certifications\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Rajkot, Gujarat, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Groww Capital India!",
